content:
Assign Analytics for Communications-Business Permissions

Available in: Developer edition and for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

From Setup, enter Users, and then select Users.
Click the name of the user.
Click Permission Set Assignments, and then click Edit Assignments.
To assign admin permission, select CRM Analytics Plus Admin and CRM for Comms Admin permission sets.
To assign user permissions, select CRM Analytics Plus User and CRM for Comms User permission sets.
Add the permission sets, and then save your changes.
title: Assigning Permissions in Salesforce CRM Analytics
